nodes.title: Click the ? icons!
widgets_values:
This  workflow is a tutorial explaining the Flex Feature system introduced by this node pack. At a high level, it works as follows:

1 We get information from a source  (the feature)
2 We use that information to control a target

Simple as that! 

There are many sources for features, and many more targets to control, and they are all interchangeable.

Click the ? icons!!





https://github.com/ryanontheinside/ComfyUI_RyanOnTheInside

Step 2, optionally, you can shape your feature output all nice-like


Click the ? icons!!

Step 3, you pick a target. Thus far, there are three categories of targets as shown below. If the category is Mask, you feed it a mask. If the category is Image, you feed it images. Otherwise, just give it the feature data

There are lots of settings, and lots of cool things, so don't forget...
CLICK THE ? ICONS!!

Love you
Ryan
